              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Worst factory: Daikibo-Factory-Seiko (480 mins)</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Most broken machines: LaserWelder &amp; LaserCutter</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
