                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Worst factory: Daikibo-Factory-Seiko (480 mins)</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Most broken machines: LaserWelder &amp; LaserCutter</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Critical zone: Seiko Section-4 (100% of Seiko downtime)</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Healthiest: Daikibo-Berlin (only 20 mins)</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Asia accounts for 97% of total downtime</run>
